OL,6,GI've often criticised Channel 4 but
OL,7,Gas many will have realised it's tough
OL,8,Glove.
OL,10,FThe remnants of the C4 of old can
OL,11,Fstill shine even when so much of the
OL,12,Fmodern channel is predictable,
OL,13,Fprovocative in a bad way or puerile.
OL,15,FAnd so it's with real pleasure I
OL,16,Foffer praise where praise is due.
OL,18,FThe new idents are absolutely
OL,19,Fexcellent.
OL,3,CNew idents reflect what Channel 4
OL,4,Cshould be about
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/4
