OL,6,FVisually they are a treat and their
OL,7,Fvalues speak to what Channel 4 should
OL,8,Freally be about.
OL,10,FThe C4 logo is bold and proud. It's a
OL,11,Flovely touch to see the 1982 colour
OL,12,Fscheme return in some of the
OL,13,Fsequences.
OL,15,FI always felt that 4 giant
OL,16,Funintentionally symbolised some of
OL,17,Fwhat was wrong with modern C4.
OL,3,CNew idents reflect what Channel 4
OL,4,Cshould be about
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
