OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F342A1687270626
OL,6,FAlthough cleverly executed, they
OL,7,Flacked depth and authority. They
OL,8,Fseemed lightweight and
OL,9,F inconsequential even with some
OL,10,Fheavier stuff awkwardly tacked on.
OL,11,FLike much of modern C4 they seemed
OL,12,Ftrivial ` but you could imagine
OL,13,Fsomeone claiming it was triviality
OL,14,Fwith a purpose.
OL,16,FThe new idents are night and day in
OL,17,Fcomparison.
OL,19,FThe launch film and accompanying poem
OL,20,Fwere also statements of what should
OL,21,Fmake C4 stand out from the crowd.
OL,3,CNew idents reflect what Channel 4
OL,4,Cshould be about
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/4
