OL,6,FAnd who ever thought there'd be an
OL,7,Fident package again based around
OL,8,Fperpetual motion?
OL,10,FAll in all these must be the best
OL,11,Fidents produced for any major channel
OL,12,Fsince the 90s.
OL,14,FLet's hope the bold new identity
OL,15,Fmight lead to bolder broadcasting by
OL,16,FC4 once its current financial
OL,17,Fdifficulties are over.
OL,3,CNew idents reflect what Channel 4
OL,4,Cshould be about
